content.text: table is designed to store detailed budget line information associated with invoice contracts. Each record in this table represents a specific budget line item linked to an invoice contract, capturing financial allocations and adjustments. The table includes fields for budget codes, financial amounts, and metadata about the creation and modification of each record.
The complexity of this table is considered medium due to the following factors:
It includes a primary key and a foreign key relationship.
It has multiple columns with default values and user-defined functions.
The table structure involves financial data types and varchar fields for various codes and identifiers.
It includes a clustered primary key index.
